      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it's honestly in such great shape. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs smoothly and is ready for all your upcoming adventures. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels wonderful, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
