    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a meticulously maintained 2008 Porsche Cayman S, featuring the robust 3.4L flat-six power plant with VarioCam Plus. This mid-engine platform delivers exceptional rotational inertia balance, paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox for optimal driver engagement. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a factory-spec McPherson strut arrangement and staggered 19-inch alloys. Recent service includes a comprehensive borescope inspection to verify cylinder wall integrity and a fresh high-temp fluid flush for the 4-piston Brembo monobloc braking system. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp, making this a quintessential driver\u2019s specimen.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
