    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i finished in a sophisticated Mineral White Metallic. This vehicle has been treated with care, serving as a reliable and luxurious daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though it shows minor, expected road wear on the front bumper consistent with its age. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in premium tires with significant tread life remaining. Inside, the Black Dakota leather interior is in excellent shape; the bolsters are firm, the surfaces are clean, and it has remained a strictly non-smoking environment. Every electronic feature, including the Harman Kardon surround sound system, navigation, and heated seats, operates perfectly. Mechanically, this sedan is sound, powered by the smooth and potent B58 inline-six engine. It has been serviced exclusively at scheduled intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. There are no leaks, no warning lights, and the transmission shifts through all gears with precision. This is a solid, honest example of German engineering that offers a refined driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
