    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape. It runs super smoothly and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a quality vehicle that\u2019s ready for the road. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll enjoy driving it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 33800.0,
