    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has undergone documented IMS bearing and rear main seal updates to ensure long-term drivetrain integrity. The chassis retains its signature communicative feedback via a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers. The exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, while the interior remains a focused cockpit with firm bolsters and precise switchgear. A mechanically honest example for the purist seeking authentic rear-engine dynamics.",
